rm=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.62</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n51269.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">warp fixed to the beam</tr_>: hence, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the web</tr_> itself, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἱστὸν ὕφαινε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:125\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.125</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἠματίη μὲν ὑφαίνεσκεν μέγαν ἱ., νύκτας δ᾽ ἀλλύεσκεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:2:104\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.104</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἱ. μεταχειρίζεσθαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg004.perseus-grc1:84a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phd.\">Phd.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">84a</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁ ἐκτετμημένος ἱ.</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the web</tr_> cut from the loom and finished, opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁ πρὸς ἐκτομήν</foreign>, Artem.l.c.; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">web of a certain size, piece,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PHib.\">PHib.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.67.12</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iii B.C.)</date>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὀθονίων ἱ. τπρισχίλιοι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:89:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.89.2</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τρεῖς ἱ. καθελεῖν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0099.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:6:20\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Str.\">Str.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.6.20</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n51269.4\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἱ. ἀραχνᾶν</foreign> spiders' <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">webs</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0199.tlg001:3:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ B.\">B.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.7</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n51269.5\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">comb</tr_> of bees, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:624a:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HA\">HA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">624a5</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n51269.6\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">shinbone, leg</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0024.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:408\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Opp.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">C.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.408</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"IV\" id=\"n51269.7\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> a constellation, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0718.tlg003:164\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aët.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.164</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}